turns.userPrompt:
Create the database schema for our task management app. We need:
- Users table (id, email, password_hash, name, avatar_url, created_at)
- Projects table (id, name, description, color, owner_id, created_at)
- Tasks table (id, title, description, project_id, assignee_id, status, priority, due_date, created_at, updated_at)
- Project_members table (project_id, user_id, role, joined_at)

Set up Prisma ORM with these models and create migrations. Include seed data with 2 users, 3 projects, and 10 tasks.
